WEBVTT

00:00:02.739 --> 00:00:04.175
<i>[singing voice] Aniplex.</i>

00:00:08.483 --> 00:00:11.422
[birds chirping]

00:00:12.191 --> 00:00:13.694
[Yakumo] So, Tatsuya,

00:00:13.761 --> 00:00:15.497
the word on the street
is that you've obtained

00:00:15.565 --> 00:00:16.834
a rare item.

00:00:16.901 --> 00:00:18.704
I'm just holding on to it.

00:00:19.238 --> 00:00:20.407
Interesting.

00:00:20.474 --> 00:00:22.512
Then return it as soon
as possible.

00:00:22.579 --> 00:00:23.681
[both gasping]

00:00:24.950 --> 00:00:26.252
Just as I suspected.

00:00:26.319 --> 00:00:27.889
It is being targeted.

00:00:27.956 --> 00:00:30.862
Yes, and these thieves
are quite good at what they do.

00:00:30.929 --> 00:00:32.231
Knowing that,

00:00:32.298 --> 00:00:34.870
let me give you
a friendly piece of advice.

00:00:35.237 --> 00:00:36.640
When you're facing the enemy,

00:00:36.707 --> 00:00:38.844
take extra care never
to lose your bearings.

00:00:38.911 --> 00:00:39.913
Do you understand?

00:00:40.180 --> 00:00:41.517
What do you mean,

00:00:41.584 --> 00:00:43.019
lose our bearings?

00:00:43.453 --> 00:00:46.326
[Yakumo] Sadly, I can't divulge
<i>anything else.</i>

00:00:49.967 --> 00:00:52.906
<i>[Rin singing in Japanese]</i>

00:00:52.973 --> 00:00:55.845
<i>[Rin Akatsuki's "Konotede"]</i>

00:00:55.912 --> 00:01:03.059
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:01:18.891 --> 00:01:25.805
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:01:47.983 --> 00:01:55.130
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:02:27.361 --> 00:02:28.631
[Tatsuya grunts]

00:02:29.332 --> 00:02:30.702
We're being followed.

00:02:30.768 --> 00:02:31.937
By what?
A car?

00:02:32.004 --> 00:02:33.239
A raven.

00:02:36.780 --> 00:02:38.651
Is that a familiar?

00:02:38.718 --> 00:02:39.886
Yes,

00:02:39.953 --> 00:02:42.358
but I don't want to reveal
my powers just yet.

00:02:42.859 --> 00:02:44.395
Hang on tight, Miyuki.

00:02:44.462 --> 00:02:46.099
[engine revving]
[gasps]

00:02:46.165 --> 00:02:47.669
[tires squealing]

00:02:52.645 --> 00:02:54.148
<i>[Ushiyama] Before you start</i>
<i>freaking out,</i>

00:02:54.215 --> 00:02:55.785
just unplug from the Internet.

00:02:55.852 --> 00:02:58.023
Disconnected!
Number 10's offline.

00:02:58.089 --> 00:03:00.227
We've successfully identified
the hacking route.

00:03:00.293 --> 00:03:02.632
Launching our
counter‐hack program.

00:03:02.699 --> 00:03:05.037
[Man] Now checking
for other vulnerable pathways.

00:03:05.103 --> 00:03:06.439
So should I reconnect?

00:03:06.507 --> 00:03:07.307
Not yet.

00:03:07.374 --> 00:03:08.476
Wait for confirmation

00:03:08.544 --> 00:03:10.247
that we've stopped the hack
[gasps]

00:03:10.313 --> 00:03:12.585
Hey, young master!

00:03:12.652 --> 00:03:14.155
Don't stop what you're doing,
please!

00:03:14.221 --> 00:03:15.357
Just continue monitoring!

00:03:15.424 --> 00:03:17.027
all: Right!

00:03:17.394 --> 00:03:18.864
Has the network been hacked?

00:03:18.931 --> 00:03:20.267
Yes, that's it.

00:03:20.333 --> 00:03:21.970
Something about this
is bugging me.

00:03:22.037 --> 00:03:24.810
This digital intrusion
is such a large scale attack

00:03:24.876 --> 00:03:27.281
and yet I still have zero idea
what they're after.

00:03:27.849 --> 00:03:29.185
You can't think
of anything stored

00:03:29.251 --> 00:03:30.555
at the lab they would want?

00:03:30.621 --> 00:03:32.759
Unauthorized access stopped.

00:03:32.826 --> 00:03:34.563
[Ushiyama] Don't let
your guard down, team!

00:03:34.629 --> 00:03:37.367
For the rest of the day,
we're staying on full alert.

00:03:37.434 --> 00:03:39.472
Ah, my apologies.

00:03:39.539 --> 00:03:40.808
So what brings you here today?

00:03:40.875 --> 00:03:42.746
You have another magical
breakthrough?

00:03:42.812 --> 00:03:44.883
I brought something I
was planning

00:03:44.950 --> 00:03:46.452
to keep at this facility.

00:03:52.397 --> 00:03:53.601
[whirring]

00:03:54.034 --> 00:03:54.936
[grunts]

00:03:56.038 --> 00:03:57.675
[booming]

00:03:57.742 --> 00:03:58.611
[hissing]

00:03:58.677 --> 00:04:00.113
Our tracer has been destroyed.

00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:01.583
Doesn't matter.

00:04:01.650 --> 00:04:04.088
What does matter is we learned
Tatsuya Shiba brought

00:04:04.155 --> 00:04:06.058
the Nino Magatama relic
to FLT.

00:04:06.125 --> 00:04:08.898
Sir, Four Leaves Technology
is counter‐attacking us.

00:04:08.964 --> 00:04:11.402
How predictable.
Cut off our lines as scheduled.

00:04:11.469 --> 00:04:13.006
I'm positive we've
thoroughly shaken

00:04:13.072 --> 00:04:15.143
Tatsuya Shiba's faith
in that lab's security

00:04:15.210 --> 00:04:16.112
by this point.

00:04:16.179 --> 00:04:17.715
I agree.

00:04:17.782 --> 00:04:20.353
[Chen] I don't foresee a kid
that intelligent leaving such

00:04:20.420 --> 00:04:23.026
a powerful o‐part
at an insecure facility.

00:04:23.092 --> 00:04:25.965
[Lu] Logically speaking,
I suppose that would be true.

00:04:26.032 --> 00:04:28.436
I already know
what you're thinking.

00:04:28.504 --> 00:04:31.409
If Tatsuya has left
the relic within their grasp,

00:04:31.476 --> 00:04:33.246
then all we have to do
is find a way

00:04:33.313 --> 00:04:34.850
to obtain the data from the lab.

00:04:34.916 --> 00:04:36.085
[scoffs]

00:04:36.152 --> 00:04:37.655
And speaking of Tatsuya,

00:04:37.722 --> 00:04:39.893
Zhou will be checking on
his classmates soon.

00:04:41.262 --> 00:04:43.166
Get rid of that girl
before he does.

00:04:43.233 --> 00:04:44.769
Right.

00:04:45.671 --> 00:04:47.407
[Tatsuya] Yes.
Understood.

00:04:47.909 --> 00:04:49.746
For your sake,
Miss Hirakawa,

00:04:49.813 --> 00:04:52.417
everything your sister did
will be swept under the rug.

00:04:52.484 --> 00:04:54.589
Huh?
[door closes]

00:04:54.656 --> 00:04:56.660
Hacking's a very serious crime,
you know.

00:04:56.727 --> 00:04:57.729
[beeping]

00:04:57.795 --> 00:05:00.033
Brother, who were you just
talking to?

00:05:00.100 --> 00:05:01.904
That was Koharu Hirakawa.

00:05:01.970 --> 00:05:04.275
She sent her sister's
phone logs over to me.

00:05:04.341 --> 00:05:05.578
Uh...

00:05:05.878 --> 00:05:08.316
We need a lead.
I'll use whatever's viable.

00:05:08.383 --> 00:05:10.187
[beeping]

00:05:10.253 --> 00:05:13.961
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

00:05:14.028 --> 00:05:16.967
[rain pattering]

00:05:22.512 --> 00:05:23.981
It's raining cats and dogs.

00:05:24.048 --> 00:05:26.319
We won't be able
to do anything outside.

00:05:26.385 --> 00:05:28.122
What are you going to do today,
brother?

00:05:28.189 --> 00:05:29.258
[Tatsuya] I'm debugging

00:05:29.325 --> 00:05:30.728
at the robot
research club today,

00:05:30.795 --> 00:05:32.364
so I'll stay nice and dry.

00:05:32.932 --> 00:05:34.970
Then I'll pick you up
from student council.

00:05:35.036 --> 00:05:35.972
[Miyuki] All right.

00:05:37.307 --> 00:05:38.811
Good luck.
Have fun.

00:05:38.878 --> 00:05:40.046
See ya later.

00:05:40.113 --> 00:05:41.917
Thanks.
I'll see you in a couple hours.

00:05:48.029 --> 00:05:49.933
Welcome, sir or madam.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:50.868
[laughs]

00:05:50.935 --> 00:05:53.172
I'm Tatsuya Shiba
of class 1‐E.

00:05:53.239 --> 00:05:54.576
[computer beeping]

00:05:54.643 --> 00:05:56.847
Authentication
process completed.

00:05:56.914 --> 00:05:58.283
[door closes]
[Tatsuya] Pixie,

00:05:58.349 --> 00:06:00.053
please stand by
in suspended mode.

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:01.389
[Pixie] Very well, master.

00:06:01.455 --> 00:06:04.563
[machine whirring]

00:06:12.044 --> 00:06:14.950
<i>[computer beeping]</i>

00:06:16.787 --> 00:06:19.158
[Tatsuya] Maybe I pushed myself
<i>too hard?</i>

00:06:19.225 --> 00:06:20.126
[computer beeps]

00:06:20.193 --> 00:06:21.162
[grunts]

00:06:21.229 --> 00:06:22.565
[gasps]

00:06:25.337 --> 00:06:26.773
<i>Sleeping gas?</i>

00:06:28.777 --> 00:06:31.984
Sir, the circulation system
has malfunctioned.

00:06:32.050 --> 00:06:33.319
Please put on this mask.

00:06:33.386 --> 00:06:34.756
It's okay.

00:06:34.823 --> 00:06:37.662
Pixie, activate
the force ventilation system.

00:06:37.729 --> 00:06:39.465
There's no fire danger.

00:06:39.899 --> 00:06:42.805
Now activating
the forced ventilation system.

00:06:42.872 --> 00:06:46.045
[whirring]

00:06:46.613 --> 00:06:48.584
<i>[Tatsuya] Pixie,</i>
<i>remain in monitoring mode</i>

00:06:48.651 --> 00:06:50.988
<i>and log the activities</i>
<i>inside this room.</i>

00:06:51.055 --> 00:06:53.694
Also, as we prepare
for the arrival of rescuers,

00:06:53.761 --> 00:06:55.497
I forbid you
from eliminating them.

00:06:55.564 --> 00:06:57.635
Yes.
Understood, master.

00:07:12.932 --> 00:07:13.901
[Isao] Shiba.

00:07:15.103 --> 00:07:16.205
Hey, Shiba.

00:07:16.673 --> 00:07:18.042
Did you fall asleep?

00:07:23.654 --> 00:07:25.357
[Kanon] Just what do you think
you're doing?

00:07:25.423 --> 00:07:26.425
[gasps]

00:07:26.492 --> 00:07:27.895
[groans]

00:07:28.296 --> 00:07:29.431
[Isao] Chiyoda!

00:07:29.498 --> 00:07:31.536
Can't say I'm surprised.

00:07:31.603 --> 00:07:33.574
You've turned industrial spy.

00:07:33.641 --> 00:07:35.377
You're way out of line, Chiyoda!

00:07:35.443 --> 00:07:37.982
I was making a backup!
That's all, okay?

00:07:38.049 --> 00:07:39.418
[Kanon] You were using
a hacking tool

00:07:39.485 --> 00:07:41.957
to make a backup?
Doesn't seem likely.

00:07:42.024 --> 00:07:43.259
Right, Shiba?

00:07:43.326 --> 00:07:45.063
[gasps]

00:07:45.130 --> 00:07:47.367
[Isao] No way!
So the gas didn't work?

00:07:47.434 --> 00:07:48.871
Isao Sekimoto,

00:07:48.937 --> 00:07:51.309
remove your CAD
and place it on the floor!

00:07:51.375 --> 00:07:52.612
[snarls]

00:07:52.679 --> 00:07:54.516
Kanon Chiyoda!

00:07:54.582 --> 00:07:58.056
[groaning]

00:07:58.122 --> 00:07:59.425
[thuds]

00:07:59.859 --> 00:08:01.295
[Kanon] Calling out
your enemy's name.

00:08:01.362 --> 00:08:02.598
How pointless.

00:08:02.965 --> 00:08:05.738
Though you always did try
too hard to be cool, Sekimoto.

00:08:09.846 --> 00:08:11.583
<i>[Mari] Listen, now Tsugu,</i>

00:08:11.650 --> 00:08:13.386
I really am sorry.

00:08:13.453 --> 00:08:15.156
I brought you on
a first time outer

00:08:15.223 --> 00:08:16.158
when you're already so busy.

00:08:16.225 --> 00:08:18.162
Don't worry.
That's what friends do.

00:08:18.229 --> 00:08:20.100
But you ship out early
tomorrow morning.

00:08:20.166 --> 00:08:21.202
You have to get ready.

00:08:21.268 --> 00:08:23.741
No, I want to spend
the day with you, Mari.

00:08:23.807 --> 00:08:26.045
Honestly, don't feel bad.
I chose to be here.

00:08:26.112 --> 00:08:27.014
[stammering]

00:08:27.080 --> 00:08:28.049
Come on.

00:08:28.116 --> 00:08:29.118
You don't have
to put it like that.

00:08:29.184 --> 00:08:31.690
Such an embarrassing thing
to say.

00:08:31.757 --> 00:08:33.393
[elevator humming]

00:08:33.459 --> 00:08:35.063
[door chimes]

00:08:38.637 --> 00:08:39.839
[gasps]

00:08:47.588 --> 00:08:49.358
[grunts]

00:08:49.425 --> 00:08:53.299
[alarm blaring]

00:08:53.366 --> 00:08:54.502
A fire?

00:08:54.569 --> 00:08:55.871
[Naotsugu] No,
it's the riot alarm.

00:08:55.938 --> 00:08:58.544
‐ It's up on the fourth floor.
‐ [Mari] The fourth?

00:08:58.744 --> 00:09:00.280
Hey, wait.
Is that girl we came to see

00:09:00.346 --> 00:09:02.117
from your school on
the fourth floor also?

00:09:02.184 --> 00:09:03.019
[grunts]

00:09:03.086 --> 00:09:04.856
[Naotsugu] Let's go!
[grunts]

00:09:05.323 --> 00:09:06.425
[grunts]

00:09:06.492 --> 00:09:08.362
Hmm?
[grunts]

00:09:08.429 --> 00:09:09.966
[Lu groaning]

00:09:10.033 --> 00:09:11.235
[grunting]

00:09:11.302 --> 00:09:14.542
[Lu grunting]

00:09:14.609 --> 00:09:18.149
[grunting]

00:09:18.216 --> 00:09:19.218
Hmm.

00:09:19.284 --> 00:09:21.990
The Man‐Eating Tiger?
You're Lu Ganghu!

00:09:23.192 --> 00:09:24.328
Illusion Blade.

00:09:24.394 --> 00:09:25.898
You're Naotsugu Chiba.

00:09:26.533 --> 00:09:28.202
[grunts]

00:09:28.269 --> 00:09:29.939
[growling]

00:09:30.006 --> 00:09:31.041
[gasps]

00:09:35.250 --> 00:09:36.218
[grunts]

00:09:36.285 --> 00:09:37.320
[shouts]

00:09:39.526 --> 00:09:41.262
[grunting]

00:09:41.328 --> 00:09:42.497
[both grunting]

00:09:42.565 --> 00:09:45.437
[shouts]

00:09:45.504 --> 00:09:46.573
[groans]

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:47.708
[gasps]

00:09:47.775 --> 00:09:49.344
[grunting]

00:09:49.411 --> 00:09:50.948
[gasping]

00:09:51.015 --> 00:09:54.488
[grunting]

00:09:54.556 --> 00:09:56.258
[both grunting]

00:09:58.162 --> 00:10:01.268
[both grunting]

00:10:05.276 --> 00:10:06.847
[gasping]

00:10:07.682 --> 00:10:09.351
[grunts]

00:10:09.418 --> 00:10:11.122
[both grunting]

00:10:12.190 --> 00:10:15.130
[groaning]

00:10:15.664 --> 00:10:17.134
[groans]

00:10:17.668 --> 00:10:20.508
[snarls]

00:10:20.574 --> 00:10:21.743
Hmm?

00:10:24.883 --> 00:10:26.051
[beeping]
[grunts]

00:10:27.387 --> 00:10:29.024
[grunts]
[booming]

00:10:29.526 --> 00:10:31.596
[shouting]

00:10:31.663 --> 00:10:33.466
[breathing heavily]

00:10:33.534 --> 00:10:35.604
[grunting]

00:10:35.671 --> 00:10:40.881
[shouting]

00:10:41.883 --> 00:10:43.754
‐ [groans]
‐ You're hurt!

00:10:43.821 --> 00:10:45.758
I'm okay.
I owe you one.

00:10:45.825 --> 00:10:47.728
[Mari] But Naotsugu,
your arm!

00:10:47.795 --> 00:10:49.164
Really, it's fine.

00:10:49.833 --> 00:10:52.003
Anyway, what was he doing here?

00:10:52.905 --> 00:10:54.341
[Mari] I have no idea.

00:10:54.408 --> 00:10:56.145
Who even was that guy?

00:10:56.546 --> 00:10:58.349
His name is Lu Ganghu.

00:10:58.416 --> 00:10:59.752
Man‐Eating Tiger.

00:10:59.819 --> 00:11:01.288
He's with
the Great Asian Alliance

00:11:01.355 --> 00:11:02.658
special ops force.

00:11:03.159 --> 00:11:06.065
That magician just now
was really him?

00:11:08.904 --> 00:11:10.440
<i>There was a break‐in</i>
<i>at the school?</i>

00:11:10.508 --> 00:11:12.277
Yes, however we thwarted it.

00:11:12.344 --> 00:11:15.350
Chiyoda assisted and I also had
the humanoid home helper

00:11:15.416 --> 00:11:16.653
recording everything.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:19.692
I'm sending you the video files.
Can you please look into it?

00:11:19.759 --> 00:11:21.028
<i>Tell me.</i>
<i>Why is it I get</i>

00:11:21.095 --> 00:11:22.532
<i>the sneaking suspicion</i>
<i>you're hinting</i>

00:11:22.598 --> 00:11:23.834
<i>that you're about</i>
<i>to finish off the fox,</i>

00:11:23.901 --> 00:11:24.903
<i>so to say?</i>

00:11:24.969 --> 00:11:26.205
That's quite the metaphor,

00:11:26.272 --> 00:11:28.242
though I never meant
to put it so arrogantly.

00:11:28.309 --> 00:11:30.213
But yeah,
something to that effect.

00:11:30.648 --> 00:11:32.117
[Kyouko] No need
to sound offended.

00:11:32.183 --> 00:11:34.021
<i>Besides,</i>
<i>the captain's already told me</i>

00:11:34.087 --> 00:11:35.691
<i>to get this wrapped up</i>
<i>sooner than later.</i>

00:11:35.758 --> 00:11:37.862
So please stay tuned.

00:11:38.697 --> 00:11:40.935
[beeping]
[knocking]

00:11:42.137 --> 00:11:43.439
[car door opens]

00:11:43.507 --> 00:11:45.844
<i>Apologies for making you wait</i>
<i>out here, Mr. Chiba.</i>

00:11:45.911 --> 00:11:47.582
<i>It was a private phone call.</i>

00:11:47.648 --> 00:11:50.286
<i>[Toshikazu] Oh, no worries.</i>
<i>That's all right.</i>

00:11:50.754 --> 00:11:53.025
However, I admit I am curious.

00:11:53.092 --> 00:11:55.463
What sort of intel did your
private informant pass along?

00:11:55.531 --> 00:11:58.637
They E‐mailed me a drawing
of a sad little mouse

00:11:58.704 --> 00:12:00.373
who was tricked by a fox
which included

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:02.177
the tail that was lent
to this poor rodent.

00:12:02.244 --> 00:12:04.248
To the collaborator was caught
on video using

00:12:04.314 --> 00:12:06.886
a hacking device.
Wait, right?

00:12:06.953 --> 00:12:08.155
That's right.

00:12:08.222 --> 00:12:10.393
The time has come for me
to embark on a fox hunt,

00:12:10.460 --> 00:12:12.197
and it would make the chase
a lot easier

00:12:12.264 --> 00:12:14.268
if I could bring
a certain hound dog with me.

00:12:14.334 --> 00:12:16.038
[chuckles]

00:12:19.979 --> 00:12:21.816
The situation has changed now.

00:12:21.883 --> 00:12:23.085
[Lu grunts]

00:12:23.553 --> 00:12:25.691
[Chen] Isao Sekimoto has failed
his mission

00:12:25.758 --> 00:12:27.862
and was taken into custody.

00:12:27.929 --> 00:12:30.400
He's in the Hachijouji
Detention Center.

00:12:31.068 --> 00:12:33.941
I've decided Chiyaki Hirakawa
can wait.

00:12:34.007 --> 00:12:36.478
Now dispose of Isao Sekimoto.

00:12:37.314 --> 00:12:38.382
Right.

00:12:45.531 --> 00:12:48.369
[birds chirping]

00:12:48.436 --> 00:12:49.371
No way.

00:12:50.841 --> 00:12:52.645
Could you at least tell me
the reason why?

00:12:52.712 --> 00:12:54.348
It doesn't matter.
No means no.

00:12:54.414 --> 00:12:56.519
[Tatsuya] Yes,
but again, why now?

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:58.790
Requests to visit
the detention center

00:12:58.857 --> 00:13:01.028
are made through the chairman
of the disciplinary committee

00:13:01.095 --> 00:13:02.364
or the student council.

00:13:02.732 --> 00:13:05.403
Yet the ultimate decision lies
with the school faculty.

00:13:05.771 --> 00:13:09.011
So you can understand why being
sent packing for no reason

00:13:09.077 --> 00:13:10.514
wouldn't sit well with me.

00:13:11.148 --> 00:13:12.985
Fine.
Because it would be a hassle.

00:13:13.185 --> 00:13:14.354
[Tatsuya] Why do you say that?

00:13:14.421 --> 00:13:16.358
We can't be certain that nothing
will happen!

00:13:16.425 --> 00:13:17.928
You don't seem to be aware
of this,

00:13:17.995 --> 00:13:19.632
so I'm going to lay it on
the line now.

00:13:19.699 --> 00:13:22.070
You're trouble.
Or rather, trouble loves you.

00:13:22.137 --> 00:13:23.472
It actively gravitates
towards you.

00:13:23.540 --> 00:13:25.811
So don't give me any extra work
when I'm already swamped.

00:13:25.878 --> 00:13:26.780
Do you hear me, Shiba?

00:13:26.846 --> 00:13:28.249
[gasping]

00:13:28.316 --> 00:13:30.286
‐ [Mari] Hang on, you guys.
‐ [grunts]

00:13:30.353 --> 00:13:32.758
It just so happens that Mayumi
and I are going

00:13:32.825 --> 00:13:34.461
to check on Sakimoto tomorrow,

00:13:34.529 --> 00:13:37.167
and there should be any problem
if he comes with us, right?

00:13:37.535 --> 00:13:40.273
Okay, only if he's going
with you two.

00:13:40.340 --> 00:13:42.377
Do you also agree
with that, Tatsuya?

00:13:42.444 --> 00:13:44.481
Even though it's not quite
the same as bringing all

00:13:44.549 --> 00:13:45.884
your close buddies alone?

00:13:48.590 --> 00:13:51.663
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:13:51.730 --> 00:13:53.032
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:13:53.099 --> 00:13:54.468
[exhales sharply]

00:13:54.535 --> 00:13:56.238
[knocking]

00:13:56.305 --> 00:13:57.474
[whimpers]

00:13:57.541 --> 00:14:00.079
[knocking]
[gasps]

00:14:01.281 --> 00:14:02.250
[beeps]

00:14:07.293 --> 00:14:10.133
[Zhou] How are you feeling
this afternoon, Miss Chiaki?

00:14:10.199 --> 00:14:12.103
Mr. Zhou,
how did you get in here?

00:14:12.170 --> 00:14:14.776
I employed my special technique.

00:14:15.143 --> 00:14:16.679
Special technique?

00:14:16.746 --> 00:14:18.015
Some kind of magic?

00:14:18.082 --> 00:14:19.719
Even without magic,

00:14:19.786 --> 00:14:21.221
humans are still capable

00:14:21.288 --> 00:14:23.059
of working all sorts
of miracles.

00:14:23.125 --> 00:14:26.331
Hey, uh,
I'm sorry, Mr. Zhou.

00:14:26.398 --> 00:14:28.537
Even though you went above
and beyond to help me

00:14:28.603 --> 00:14:29.639
and gave me advice,

00:14:29.706 --> 00:14:32.277
I couldn't complete my mission.

00:14:32.845 --> 00:14:34.381
[gasps]

00:14:35.818 --> 00:14:37.855
Don't worry your pretty
little head about that,

00:14:37.922 --> 00:14:39.124
Miss Chiaki.

00:14:39.191 --> 00:14:41.295
If, however,
for some strange reason,

00:14:41.361 --> 00:14:43.934
you do come
to regret your failure,

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:46.773
and if the memory becomes
a burden to you,

00:14:46.840 --> 00:14:50.213
then perhaps it's best
you simply forget about me.

00:14:51.950 --> 00:14:53.018
Right.

00:14:53.085 --> 00:14:54.655
I'll forget about you.

00:14:56.458 --> 00:14:57.962
<i>[Mari] How's the prep</i>
<i>for the thesis competition,</i>

00:14:58.028 --> 00:14:59.297
<i>Tatsuya?</i>

00:14:59.364 --> 00:15:00.701
<i>Isn't that coming up</i>
<i>this weekend?</i>

00:15:00.768 --> 00:15:02.538
[Tatsuya] It's going well since
<i>I've already completed</i>

00:15:02.605 --> 00:15:04.040
<i>my share of the work.</i>

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:08.784
[door opens]
[Mayumi] Tatsuya.

00:15:08.850 --> 00:15:10.453
You'll need to come
in here with me.

00:15:20.908 --> 00:15:22.277
[groans]

00:15:22.343 --> 00:15:24.247
[door opens]
[gasps]

00:15:24.314 --> 00:15:25.483
[shouts]

00:15:25.551 --> 00:15:26.619
[Isao] Watanabe!

00:15:29.759 --> 00:15:31.228
What are you doing here?

00:15:32.263 --> 00:15:34.635
I came to hear your explanation,
Sekimoto.

00:15:34.702 --> 00:15:36.873
Not even you can use magic
in the confines

00:15:36.940 --> 00:15:38.142
of this jail cell.

00:15:38.476 --> 00:15:39.612
Oh, really?

00:15:39.679 --> 00:15:43.820
[magical whirring]

00:15:43.887 --> 00:15:50.834
[groans]

00:15:50.901 --> 00:15:52.805
[exhales]

00:15:52.872 --> 00:15:56.178
[Tatsuya] Is that scent‐based
mind control she's using?

00:15:56.245 --> 00:15:58.717
Oh, is this your first time
seeing it in action?

00:15:58.783 --> 00:16:00.253
Yes.

00:16:00.319 --> 00:16:02.056
<i>[Isao] After copying over</i>
<i>the data from</i>

00:16:02.123 --> 00:16:03.727
<i>the demo machine,</i>

00:16:03.793 --> 00:16:06.633
<i>I was supposed to go through</i>
<i>Shiba's personal belongings.</i>

00:16:06.699 --> 00:16:09.237
<i>And what's in his possession</i>
<i>that you're after?</i>

00:16:10.206 --> 00:16:11.976
<i>I must retrieve the relic.</i>

00:16:12.043 --> 00:16:14.014
That's insane.
You don't have that, do you?

00:16:14.080 --> 00:16:15.784
Uh, no.

00:16:15.851 --> 00:16:16.820
[alarm blaring]

00:16:16.886 --> 00:16:18.189
[grunts]

00:16:21.128 --> 00:16:22.463
[Mari] Tatsuya!

00:16:24.000 --> 00:16:25.737
It seems there's an intruder.

00:16:26.906 --> 00:16:28.510
He may be after Sekimoto.

00:16:28.577 --> 00:16:29.512
[gasps]

00:16:35.022 --> 00:16:36.626
It's the Man‐Eating Tiger.

00:16:36.693 --> 00:16:37.895
[gasps]

00:16:37.962 --> 00:16:39.665
[snarls]

00:16:41.068 --> 00:16:42.538
[grunts]

00:16:43.372 --> 00:16:45.309
I'd say we should try
to make an escape,

00:16:45.376 --> 00:16:47.815
but it looks like
it's a little too late.

00:16:48.482 --> 00:16:50.787
Tatsuya, you protect Mayumi
no matter what.

00:16:50.854 --> 00:16:52.023
[gasps]

00:16:52.892 --> 00:16:54.996
Don't do anything too dangerous.

00:16:58.168 --> 00:17:00.406
I won't.
I know he's no ordinary foe.

00:17:00.841 --> 00:17:02.545
[beeping]

00:17:02.611 --> 00:17:04.147
[whirring]

00:17:09.926 --> 00:17:11.596
[both grunting]

00:17:11.663 --> 00:17:14.100
[magical whirring]

00:17:15.169 --> 00:17:17.073
[grunting]

00:17:17.140 --> 00:17:19.177
[both grunting]

00:17:19.946 --> 00:17:21.048
Huh?

00:17:21.114 --> 00:17:22.050
[groans]

00:17:22.116 --> 00:17:23.520
[grunts]

00:17:23.587 --> 00:17:25.591
[grunting]

00:17:28.630 --> 00:17:32.805
[grunts]

00:17:33.640 --> 00:17:35.711
[both grunting]

00:17:37.881 --> 00:17:38.883
[grunts]

00:17:39.150 --> 00:17:40.319
Hah!

00:17:41.623 --> 00:17:42.758
[grunts]

00:17:42.925 --> 00:17:43.860
[gasps]

00:17:43.927 --> 00:17:45.129
[grunts]

00:17:45.463 --> 00:17:46.398
‐ [shouts]
‐ [gasps]

00:17:46.465 --> 00:17:47.835
‐ [gasps]
‐ [snarling]

00:17:49.605 --> 00:17:54.314
[yelling]

00:17:59.090 --> 00:18:03.833
[snarling]

00:18:05.136 --> 00:18:06.739
[beeping]
[grunting]

00:18:07.240 --> 00:18:10.346
[shouting]

00:18:11.816 --> 00:18:12.785
[grunts]

00:18:18.563 --> 00:18:19.966
[grunts]

00:18:20.032 --> 00:18:22.236
[groaning]

00:18:25.944 --> 00:18:27.246
[shouts]

00:18:28.783 --> 00:18:29.819
[grunts]

00:18:31.054 --> 00:18:34.629
[shouts]

00:18:34.695 --> 00:18:35.764
[thuds]

00:18:35.831 --> 00:18:37.033
[gasps]

00:18:37.100 --> 00:18:40.841
[groaning]

00:18:42.678 --> 00:18:44.649
[exhales]

00:18:45.550 --> 00:18:47.120
<i>[Kyouko] Unfortunately,</i>

00:18:47.186 --> 00:18:50.226
<i>we were unable to capture</i>
<i>their leader, Chen Xiangshan.</i>

00:18:50.292 --> 00:18:52.063
<i>Although since you</i>
<i>and your friends managed</i>

00:18:52.130 --> 00:18:53.667
<i>to apprehend Lu Ganghu,</i>

00:18:53.733 --> 00:18:57.140
<i>the 101st successfully took</i>
<i>the mobile espionage unit</i>

00:18:57.206 --> 00:18:58.510
<i>into custody</i>
<i>so I'd call that</i>

00:18:58.576 --> 00:19:00.547
<i>an overall win.</i>
<i>Thanks.</i>

00:19:00.614 --> 00:19:02.584
No, thank you.
After all,

00:19:02.651 --> 00:19:04.387
I'm the one who asked you
to investigate it.

00:19:04.454 --> 00:19:06.926
I suppose on paper that is true,
<i>sure,</i>

00:19:06.993 --> 00:19:09.765
<i>although manufacturers</i>
<i>including Izumo Electronics</i>

00:19:09.832 --> 00:19:11.468
<i>and Tsukumo Magic</i>
<i>had fallen victim</i>

00:19:11.536 --> 00:19:12.771
<i>to their thievery.</i>

00:19:13.138 --> 00:19:14.374
Is that right?

00:19:14.441 --> 00:19:16.178
By the way,
about the relic.

00:19:16.244 --> 00:19:18.215
Did you find out where
the leak originated?

00:19:18.282 --> 00:19:19.685
<i>[Kyouko] I'm embarrassed</i>
<i>to admit this,</i>

00:19:19.752 --> 00:19:23.225
but the National Defense Force's
accounting data was compromised.

00:19:23.927 --> 00:19:25.931
<i>Every single magic</i>
<i>research company</i>

00:19:25.997 --> 00:19:28.603
<i>receiving payment</i>
<i>from the army unfortunately</i>

00:19:28.670 --> 00:19:30.674
<i>was targeted</i>
<i>by these foreign spies.</i>

00:19:30.741 --> 00:19:31.909
That's too bad.

00:19:32.978 --> 00:19:34.147
Well, I know you're busy.

00:19:34.214 --> 00:19:35.349
Thanks for the update.

00:19:35.416 --> 00:19:37.353
You're certainly welcome, agent.

00:19:37.420 --> 00:19:39.257
<i>Good luck at</i>
<i>the thesis competition.</i>

00:19:39.324 --> 00:19:40.694
<i>I'm rooting for you.</i>

00:19:41.261 --> 00:19:43.700
[beeping]

00:19:48.977 --> 00:19:50.413
[exhales]

00:19:56.926 --> 00:19:57.961
[exhales]

00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:19.772
[gasps]

00:20:21.843 --> 00:20:24.782
[heart beating]

00:20:29.792 --> 00:20:31.228
[gasps]

00:20:31.829 --> 00:20:32.765
[gasps]

00:20:32.831 --> 00:20:33.933
[gasps]

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:35.537
[inhales sharply]

00:20:37.741 --> 00:20:40.212
[gasps]

00:20:41.749 --> 00:20:43.285
[gasps]

00:20:43.953 --> 00:20:45.891
[gasps]

00:20:46.826 --> 00:20:47.895
[gasps]

00:20:48.362 --> 00:20:49.598
[gasps]

00:20:49.665 --> 00:20:51.401
I'm so sorry!
Please forgive me, brother!

00:20:51.468 --> 00:20:53.840
[breathing heavily]

00:20:54.340 --> 00:20:56.411
[door opens and closes]
[exhales]

00:20:59.718 --> 00:21:01.354
<i>[Miyuki] What was I thinking?</i>

00:21:01.421 --> 00:21:03.593
<i>Did I really just do that?</i>

00:21:04.427 --> 00:21:08.703
<i>We were this close</i>
<i>to sharing a‐‐a...</i>

00:21:08.770 --> 00:21:10.540
[whimpers]

00:21:10.607 --> 00:21:12.578
‐ [Tatsuya] Miyuki?
‐ [gasps]

00:21:12.644 --> 00:21:13.780
Uh, yes?

00:21:14.582 --> 00:21:15.650
[Tatsuya] Can I come in, please?

00:21:15.717 --> 00:21:17.621
Just a moment, please, brother!

00:21:22.063 --> 00:21:24.502
Thanks for waiting.
You can come in now.

00:21:26.404 --> 00:21:27.841
[chuckles]

00:21:31.448 --> 00:21:34.855
[whimpers]

00:21:36.024 --> 00:21:37.661
[whimpers]

00:21:43.907 --> 00:21:47.313
Miyuki, you're crying.
What happened?

00:21:48.348 --> 00:21:50.821
[Tatsuya] I've made you worry
about me again, haven't I?

00:21:50.887 --> 00:21:52.223
I'm sorry.

00:21:52.758 --> 00:21:54.595
It's okay.
I was just tired.

00:21:54.662 --> 00:21:56.933
So please don't fret anymore,
Miyuki.

00:22:00.206 --> 00:22:01.676
Go to bed now,
all right?

00:22:07.153 --> 00:22:08.690
[door closes]

00:22:17.908 --> 00:22:19.778
[exhales]

00:22:20.747 --> 00:22:21.682
[gasps]

00:22:21.749 --> 00:22:28.362
[giggling]

00:22:28.830 --> 00:22:31.936
<i>[Rei singing in Japanese]</i>

00:22:32.003 --> 00:22:34.909
<i>[Rei Yasuda's "Mirror"]</i>

00:22:34.975 --> 00:22:41.923
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:23:03.265 --> 00:23:10.412
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

